OL,6,FSimon Horswell, a fraud specialist
OL,7,Fwith the Entrust organisation told us:
OL,8,F"We are now at the point where you
OL,9,Fcannot trust what you see with your
OL,10,Feyes.
OL,12,F"If you are in a video call with
OL,13,Fsomeone and you're not sure if who
OL,14,Fyou're talking to is genuine, then try
OL,15,Fand recall a personal memory that the
OL,16,Ftwo of you would have - that isn't
OL,17,Fposted online."
