OL,6,FPolice at Action Fraud, which
OL,7,Fspearheads the national fight against
OL,8,Fscams, has issued a 12 cons of
OL,9,FChristmas warning.
OL,11,FOnline shopping fraud, courier cons,
OL,12,Fgift card swindles, charity fraud,
OL,13,Fsocial media hacking and romance
OL,14,Fdeception all give criminals an
OL,15,Fopportunity to cash-in on common
OL,16,FChristmas activities.
