OL,6,FOne set of scams that peak at
OL,7,FChristmas involve bogus jobs. Mihala
OL,8,FLazar saw a social media advert for
OL,9,Fproduct reviewers.
OL,11,FMihala is determined to help others
OL,12,Favoid falling into the trap after she
OL,13,Flost almost #4,000.
OL,15,FFraud lawyers warn "'tis the season to
OL,16,Fbe scammed", Martin Richardson from
OL,17,Fthe National Fraud Helpline Solicitors
OL,18,Ftold ITV News, adding: "One of my
OL,19,Ffavourite tips is to ask a friend or a
OL,20,Ffamily member to check something out
OL,21,Fif you're slightly suspicious of it."
